title: Ask HN: How do you add headers in href of an a tag/link?
text:
Hello hackers,

I am stuck on this and I have tried all possible channels available to me. I thought maybe I can find some help here.

So, there is an API endpoint requires a token (API key). However, the full link of the API is meant to be added in the third party app and be opened in the client`s browser while also passing the header information.

For example, the API link is x.com/do_this

the client (of the API) adds the link in their application. When the client`s user clicks the link, it should open x.com/do_this but the client`s API key is needed to show some information when that link is opened.

How do I go about this? I dont mind using AJAX, JS, or any other tech out there that can provide this solution.

Thanks

title: Ask HN: How did you meet your VC
text:
Hi, I'm relatively experienced in software but have absolutely no idea how to meet a VC.

For background:

- I built a software company before & did $1M in sales.

- Me and my small team want to pivot to a better product/market

- The new product (pivoting to) automatically edits every sales meeting into a highlight-reel video & sends that as follow-up, for a guaranteed demo-deal conversion rate lift

- From the North of England not a VC hotspot

I have bootstrapped the new company with the old but need to meet a VC to get all of the way there and I have no idea how to get pitch meetings.

So I am really curious how did you meet your VCs or how do you meet a VC in general?

Show HN: Experiences with Stripe in Small Hotels
text:
First of all our service is not prohibited by Stripe, we are a small hotel.
We sell our rooms in booking and booking sends us a virtual credit card to be used to bill each customer for the room.
We withdrew the funds from the virtual credit card in the stripe platform and after two months of using it, my Stripe account was closed.
The stripe account manager told me that we had a higher than normal percentage of prepaid cards and that we may be suspected of money laundering.
Stripe has now refunded all the funds in my account (automatically)
